00:17:36,034 --> 00:17:38,328
Then what is an increasing function?

261
00:18:46,104 --> 00:18:47,522
We'll have a guest.

262
00:18:48,941 --> 00:18:49,942
A guest?

263
00:18:50,525 --> 00:18:51,485
A good guest?

264
00:18:51,568 --> 00:18:52,986
A bad guest?

265
00:18:54,363 --> 00:18:55,364
What kind of…

266
00:19:01,119 --> 00:19:01,954
What is it?

267
00:19:04,915 --> 00:19:06,458
You're scaring me.

268
00:19:08,877 --> 00:19:10,170
Should I take out my knife?

269
00:19:10,671 --> 00:19:11,672
I'm not sure.

270
00:19:13,131 --> 00:19:15,259
I can't see what kind of guest it is.

271
00:19:37,614 --> 00:19:38,532
You got this.

272
00:19:38,615 --> 00:19:41,118
Geon-woo. Get ready.

273
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:10,022
He flies on the mat,
but he always struggles in the sandpit.

274
00:20:12,024 --> 00:20:13,775
Hey, Kim Geon-woo. Come here.

275
00:20:15,777 --> 00:20:18,405
Was it that big a deal
getting disqualified last year?

276
00:20:18,488 --> 00:20:20,615
-I'm sorry.
-I'm sorry, my ass.

277
00:20:20,699 --> 00:20:24,953
You couldn't even get a proper jump-off
in competition this year.

278
00:20:25,037 --> 00:20:27,289
If this keeps up,
you'll really get the yips.

279
00:20:27,789 --> 00:20:29,499
Get a hold of yourself, okay?

280
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,918
Go. Go back to the starting line.

281
00:20:41,678 --> 00:20:43,638
Don't treat it like the real thing.

282
00:20:45,515 --> 00:20:46,975
That's easier said than done.

283
00:20:50,479 --> 00:20:51,605
Before you jump,

284
00:20:51,688 --> 00:20:53,940
close your eyes
and take a moment to think.

285
00:20:54,024 --> 00:20:55,734
"The whole world is the mat."

286
00:20:56,234 --> 00:20:57,277
"I can do this."

287
00:20:57,361 --> 00:20:58,570
Picture that,

288
00:20:58,653 --> 00:21:01,239
and when you open your eyes,
run like crazy and jump.

289
00:21:01,323 --> 00:21:03,950
Is that what you do every time you jump?

290
00:21:05,410 --> 00:21:06,286
No.

291
00:21:06,912 --> 00:21:08,246
I just jump.

292
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:20,884
Hurry!

293
00:21:20,967 --> 00:21:22,969
-Come on. We've got to go!
-Hurry!

294
00:21:23,470 --> 00:21:26,598
ASBESTOS REMOVAL IN PROGRESS
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

295
00:22:03,510 --> 00:22:06,888
Are you on any medication?
Like painkillers or cold medicine?

296
00:22:07,389 --> 00:22:09,683
No! Did someone accuse me of doping?

297
00:22:09,766 --> 00:22:11,309
Hormone shots? Birth control?

298
00:22:11,810 --> 00:22:14,688
-Coach, I swear I'd never--
-The national reserve team called.

299
00:22:16,857 --> 00:22:17,691
What?

300
00:22:20,944 --> 00:22:23,738
You should've led with that!

301
00:22:23,822 --> 00:22:26,074
So from now on,
you're in special training.

302
00:22:26,158 --> 00:22:27,159
Even on weekends.

303
00:22:27,242 --> 00:22:29,494
You gotta get better
before you join the team

304
00:22:29,578 --> 00:22:31,204
so I don't look bad.

305
00:22:31,288 --> 00:22:32,956
I'll do my best.

306
00:22:33,039 --> 00:22:34,541
Coach!

307
00:22:35,041 --> 00:22:35,959
Oh boy!

308
00:22:36,042 --> 00:22:38,295
Gross. Get off me.

309
00:22:39,588 --> 00:22:41,923
Poor you. No more weekend dates.

310
00:22:44,301 --> 00:22:47,971
Or bring Geon-woo and train with him.
Before he gets the yips.

311
00:22:53,727 --> 00:22:56,271
Coach, so you knew?

312
00:22:57,606 --> 00:22:59,858
How could I not know?

313
00:23:00,358 --> 00:23:01,568
Goodness me.

314
00:23:07,365 --> 00:23:09,284
SE-AH

315
00:23:12,996 --> 00:23:14,664
Hey, Se-ah.

316
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,001
Hello?

317
00:23:21,213 --> 00:23:22,255
Hello?

318
00:23:24,633 --> 00:23:25,800
SE-AH

319
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:27,344
What the…

320
00:23:47,531 --> 00:23:49,199
Fucking hell.

321
00:23:49,866 --> 00:23:53,537
Are you guys actually going
to that loser Choi Hyeong-wook's birthday?

322
00:23:53,620 --> 00:23:54,788
Who fucking cares?

323
00:23:54,871 --> 00:23:57,874
I'm sick of looking after him at school.
Now on weekends too?

324
00:23:57,958 --> 00:23:59,751
That dumbass is so damn annoying.

325
00:23:59,834 --> 00:24:02,045
-Oh God!
-"Having you guys there is the present."

326
00:24:02,128 --> 00:24:03,088
I fucking hate it!

327
00:24:03,171 --> 00:24:05,257
That was so fucking embarrassing.
I almost died.

328
00:24:05,340 --> 00:24:06,466
Is he out of his mind?

329
00:24:06,550 --> 00:24:08,260
He's so damn dense.

330
00:24:08,343 --> 00:24:09,886
Fucking hell.

331
00:24:09,970 --> 00:24:12,514
I wish he'd stop following us around.

332
00:24:13,014 --> 00:24:14,307
-Hey!
-I can't stand him.

333
00:24:14,391 --> 00:24:15,934
-Huh?
-You little…

334
00:24:17,143 --> 00:24:18,562
For fuck's sake.

335
00:24:19,604 --> 00:24:20,981
CALL ENDED
SE-AH

336
00:24:29,948 --> 00:24:31,116
CALLING
SE-AH

337
00:24:34,744 --> 00:24:38,206
HYEONG-WOOK

338
00:24:43,461 --> 00:24:46,172
HYEONG-WOOK

339
00:24:51,428 --> 00:24:53,680
The person you are trying to…

340
00:25:01,354 --> 00:25:02,188
Geon-woo.

341
00:25:02,689 --> 00:25:04,107
I made the national team.

342
00:25:12,407 --> 00:25:13,283
Geon-woo.

343
00:25:13,783 --> 00:25:15,952
I made the national…

344
00:25:35,805 --> 00:25:36,640
Hyeong-wook!

345
00:25:42,354 --> 00:25:44,022
Did his mom scold him again?

346
00:25:51,404 --> 00:25:53,948
Hey, what were you watching
instead of studying?

347
00:25:54,032 --> 00:25:55,700
What's that app you use? Tell us!

348
00:25:55,784 --> 00:25:58,787
What's taking you so long?
We're the last ones!

349
00:25:58,870 --> 00:25:59,704
Sorry!

350
00:25:59,788 --> 00:26:01,247
Yeah, coming!

351
00:26:14,427 --> 00:26:15,261
They're gone.

352
00:26:15,762 --> 00:26:16,805
You took a while.

353
00:26:17,389 --> 00:26:19,182
I made the national team.

354
00:26:19,265 --> 00:26:20,475
What? The national team?

355
00:26:20,558 --> 00:26:22,227
You made it! You--

356
00:26:27,315 --> 00:26:28,149
What's going on?

357
00:26:31,361 --> 00:26:32,487
You scared?

358
00:26:34,781 --> 00:26:35,865
Scared? As if.

359
00:26:36,366 --> 00:26:39,035
I'm holding your hands
because I'm proud you made it.

360
00:26:46,292 --> 00:26:47,293
National team.

361
00:26:49,462 --> 00:26:50,547
Oh, right.

362
00:26:50,630 --> 00:26:52,173
The coach knows.

363
00:26:52,674 --> 00:26:53,550
About us.

364
00:26:55,051 --> 00:26:56,386
Did you tell her?

365
00:26:56,469 --> 00:27:01,015
No. I didn't even tell Hyeong-wook,
Ha-joon, or Na-ri.

366
00:27:03,059 --> 00:27:04,269
She just knew.

367
00:27:08,815 --> 00:27:10,442
What should I do?

368
00:27:12,026 --> 00:27:13,695
I'm already on her bad side.

369
00:27:16,281 --> 00:27:17,574
I'm so screwed.

370
00:27:25,081 --> 00:27:27,500
AUNT JI-SUN,
I MADE THE NATIONAL RESERVE TEAM!

371
00:27:33,715 --> 00:27:34,883
MISSED CALLS
HYEONG-WOOK (39)

372
00:27:34,966 --> 00:27:36,259
Is something up?

373
00:27:39,679 --> 00:27:40,513
CONGRATULATIONS

374
00:27:40,597 --> 00:27:42,182
ON DUTY AGAIN, SO I WON'T BE HOME

375
00:27:42,766 --> 00:27:43,808
For myself?

376
00:27:44,309 --> 00:27:45,310
Seriously.

377
00:27:56,237 --> 00:27:58,698
UP FOR CHICKEN?

378
00:28:02,535 --> 00:28:04,746
This is so good. It seriously slaps.

379
00:28:05,413 --> 00:28:06,581
Thank you so much, Se-ah.

380
00:28:08,583 --> 00:28:09,751
Thank my aunt.

381
00:28:09,834 --> 00:28:12,754
If I meet your aunt,
I'll definitely thank her. For real.

382
00:28:12,837 --> 00:28:13,671
Sure.

383
00:28:14,631 --> 00:28:16,966
-I'm gonna brag to the others.
-Go ahead.

384
00:28:19,135 --> 00:28:20,094
Oh, right.

385
00:28:21,387 --> 00:28:24,057
I've got a bunch of missed calls
from Hyeong-wook.

386
00:28:24,641 --> 00:28:25,809
From Hyeong-wook? Why?

387
00:28:25,892 --> 00:28:27,018
No idea.

388
00:28:27,977 --> 00:28:29,062
-I'm calling him.
-Okay.

389
00:28:42,784 --> 00:28:44,202
STOP SULKING AND COME DRINK!

390
00:28:45,745 --> 00:28:51,251
HEY, I'M UNDERAGE. I CAN'T EVEN GET IN

391
00:28:53,086 --> 00:28:54,629
SEND ME YOUR ID PHOTO ON TELEGRAM

392
00:29:14,607 --> 00:29:15,650
Hey, you!

393
00:29:16,734 --> 00:29:18,319
Hey, you're here.

394
00:29:19,487 --> 00:29:21,239
This is insane.

395
00:29:21,322 --> 00:29:24,409
How did this even get past the QR?
You could totally sell these.

396
00:29:24,492 --> 00:29:26,703
Sadly, I didn't make these, so I can't.

397
00:29:26,786 --> 00:29:27,912
If not you, then who?

398
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:29,956
No way.

399
00:29:31,833 --> 00:29:32,917
Hey!

400
00:29:42,594 --> 00:29:43,595
THE REPAIR IS DONE

401
00:29:43,678 --> 00:29:46,806
I'LL SEND YOU THE TRACKING NUMBER
ONCE IT SHIPS TOMORROW

402
00:30:06,117 --> 00:30:07,493
HYEONG-WOOK

403
00:30:08,077 --> 00:30:08,912
Girigo.

404
00:30:08,995 --> 00:30:10,997
And the other perfect scorer is…

405
00:30:11,080 --> 00:30:11,956
Choi Hyeong-wook.

406
00:30:12,040 --> 00:30:13,458
No way.

407
00:30:17,086 --> 00:30:18,087
KANG HA-YOUNG

408
00:30:21,382 --> 00:30:22,550
Since when does she call?

409
00:30:34,354 --> 00:30:37,065
Hyeong-wook, you called me a bunch.
What's up?

410
00:30:37,941 --> 00:30:39,192
You called me first.

411
00:30:39,692 --> 00:30:40,526
I did?

412
00:30:41,819 --> 00:30:44,739
Hey, speak up.
I can't hear a word you're saying.

413
00:30:46,282 --> 00:30:47,116
You

414
00:30:48,451 --> 00:30:49,869
aren't coming to my party.

415
00:30:51,788 --> 00:30:53,039
Oh, right.

416
00:30:53,831 --> 00:30:54,666
Sorry.

417
00:30:55,291 --> 00:30:57,627
I just found out
I have to train this weekend.

418
00:31:00,129 --> 00:31:01,965
What the heck? Did he just hang up?

419
00:31:03,341 --> 00:31:07,762
The phone you're calling is turned off.
Please leave a message after the beep.

420
00:31:07,845 --> 00:31:10,264
Shoot. Is he upset with me?

421
00:31:11,808 --> 00:31:14,686
But how did he even know
I couldn't make it?

422
00:31:15,186 --> 00:31:16,104
Right.

423
00:31:16,646 --> 00:31:18,189
I only just found out myself.

424
00:31:21,526 --> 00:31:22,527
Sorry.

425
00:31:23,319 --> 00:31:25,530
My head has been elsewhere lately.

426
00:31:27,407 --> 00:31:30,493
Weekend training is brutal enough,
so I'll let it slide.

427
00:31:32,495 --> 00:31:34,497
Geon-woo, what are you going to do?

428
00:31:34,580 --> 00:31:37,166
Of course I'm going.
It's Hyeong-wook's birthday.

429
00:31:38,584 --> 00:31:39,419
Right.

430
00:31:40,128 --> 00:31:41,045
You should go.

431
00:31:43,506 --> 00:31:45,174
Are you worried about Na-ri?

432
00:31:46,926 --> 00:31:47,760
No, I'm not.

433
00:31:47,844 --> 00:31:48,803
No.

434
00:31:49,387 --> 00:31:50,805
Don't worry.

435
00:31:52,682 --> 00:31:54,892
Should I ask the coach
to postpone the training?

436
00:32:00,982 --> 00:32:02,066
Geon-woo.

437
00:32:02,567 --> 00:32:03,526
What are you doing?

438
00:32:04,027 --> 00:32:06,904
October 24, 2008…

439
00:32:07,405 --> 00:32:08,698
Name…

440
00:32:11,117 --> 00:32:12,076
Done.

441
00:32:17,832 --> 00:32:19,417
OCTOBER 24, 2008
KIM GEON-WOO

442
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:22,795
Please let Se-ah's training be canceled
this weekend.

443
00:32:22,879 --> 00:32:24,380
Hey, what are you doing?

444
00:32:25,089 --> 00:32:28,009
It granted a perfect score.
Canceling training should be easy.

445
00:32:29,135 --> 00:32:31,763
-Cancel the training!
-Oh, come on.

446
00:32:31,846 --> 00:32:34,348
Cancel the training! Cancel! Training!

447
00:32:34,432 --> 00:32:36,768
Cancel the training.

448
00:32:36,851 --> 00:32:40,146
-Please grant Geon-woo's wish.
-Cancel the training.

449
00:32:40,229 --> 00:32:42,732
-You believe that? You dummy.
-Cancel the training.

450
00:32:42,815 --> 00:32:44,317
Sit down and eat your chicken.

451
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,110
-Let me just send this.
-You dummy.

452
00:32:46,194 --> 00:32:48,613
SENDING WISH…

453
00:32:50,531 --> 00:32:51,657
I can't grab this one.

454
00:32:52,158 --> 00:32:53,451
-You can't?
-Yeah.

455
00:32:54,577 --> 00:32:55,453
Say ah.

456
00:33:06,964 --> 00:33:07,965
FRIDAY, JUNE 13
7:00

457
00:33:16,099 --> 00:33:17,683
SLEEPING IN AGAIN?

458
00:33:18,851 --> 00:33:19,685
JUST 5 MINUTES!

459
00:33:42,667 --> 00:33:44,335
The doors are closing.

460
00:33:47,296 --> 00:33:48,256
One more time?

461
00:33:48,339 --> 00:33:49,715
Oh, stop it!

462
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:02,270
Did they go already?

463
00:34:02,770 --> 00:34:03,646
I guess so.

464
00:34:10,570 --> 00:34:12,321
Come on, what are you talking about?

465
00:34:12,905 --> 00:34:15,491
All right. Let's get started.

466
00:34:15,575 --> 00:34:18,202
Hello.

467
00:34:18,286 --> 00:34:20,204
Let's see who's absent.

468
00:34:20,288 --> 00:34:21,414
Where's Na-ri?

469
00:34:21,914 --> 00:34:23,249
-She's not here yet?
-No.

470
00:34:23,332 --> 00:34:25,126
I don't know.

471
00:34:25,209 --> 00:34:27,086
That rascal's late again.

472
00:34:30,923 --> 00:34:33,926
Did anyone see or meet Na-ri last night?

473
00:34:35,094 --> 00:34:36,554
Not me.

474
00:34:37,180 --> 00:34:38,014
No one?

475
00:34:39,182 --> 00:34:41,100
Tell her to come see me when she arrives.

476
00:34:45,313 --> 00:34:47,231
Whoever's phone just rang, stand up.

477
00:34:49,525 --> 00:34:50,818
Hyeong-wook.

478
00:34:50,902 --> 00:34:52,028
Didn't you hear me?

479
00:34:52,111 --> 00:34:53,279
Hey.

480
00:34:53,946 --> 00:34:56,115
Hey, he's mad. Get up now.

481
00:34:56,908 --> 00:34:57,742
Hyeong-wook.

482
00:34:58,701 --> 00:35:00,536
Stop fooling around and get up.

483
00:35:01,537 --> 00:35:02,371
Hyeong-wook.

484
00:35:02,455 --> 00:35:04,415
Hey, get up already.

485
00:35:05,958 --> 00:35:07,043
Choi Hyeong-wook!

486
00:35:10,254 --> 00:35:11,964
Hey, Hyeong-wook.

487
00:35:12,673 --> 00:35:13,841
Hey, Hyeong-wook.

488
00:35:13,925 --> 00:35:15,218
Hyeong-wook!

489
00:35:15,301 --> 00:35:16,427
Hey! Sir!

490
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:17,970
Class President, get the nurse.

491
00:35:18,054 --> 00:35:18,888
-Now!
-Yes, sir!

492
00:35:18,971 --> 00:35:21,265
Stay with me. Hey, Hyeong-wook!

493
00:35:30,066 --> 00:35:30,942
Are you okay?

494
00:35:31,651 --> 00:35:32,652
-Hey.
-Huh?

495
00:35:33,277 --> 00:35:34,195
Are you okay?

496
00:35:35,321 --> 00:35:36,864
-Hey, Hyeong-wook.
-You okay?

497
00:35:36,948 --> 00:35:38,282
-You all right?
-Hyeong-wook.

498
00:35:47,959 --> 00:35:49,168
-Hey.
-Hey!

499
00:35:50,378 --> 00:35:52,129
-Stop, Hyeong-wook.
-Hyeong-wook.

500
00:35:52,213 --> 00:35:53,089
Put the knife down.

501
00:35:53,172 --> 00:35:55,132
-Hyeong-wook.
-It's dangerous!

502
00:35:55,216 --> 00:35:56,467
The knife!

503
00:35:58,469 --> 00:36:00,054
Geon-woo!

504
00:36:00,888 --> 00:36:02,181
Geon-woo!

505
00:36:04,433 --> 00:36:05,309
Hey, Hyeong-wook!

506
00:36:06,143 --> 00:36:07,186
Hyeong-wook, don't.

507
00:36:07,270 --> 00:36:08,562
Hyeong-wook.

508
00:36:13,567 --> 00:36:14,944
Don't do that!

509
00:36:15,444 --> 00:36:16,612
Hyeong-wook!

510
00:36:17,947 --> 00:36:19,448
Hyeong-wook!

511
00:36:24,578 --> 00:36:25,788
Get lost!

512
00:36:25,871 --> 00:36:27,665
I said fucking get lost!

513
00:36:30,751 --> 00:36:31,877
Hyeong-wook!

514
00:36:32,503 --> 00:36:33,337
What's wrong?

515
00:36:33,921 --> 00:36:35,131
Die!

516
00:36:49,729 --> 00:36:50,813
Help me.

517
00:36:51,439 --> 00:36:52,523
Hyeong-wook.

518
00:36:58,154 --> 00:37:00,281
Hyeong-wook, put the knife down. Okay?

519
00:37:01,991 --> 00:37:03,868
What's wrong? Hyeong-wook. Put it down.

520
00:37:05,745 --> 00:37:06,912
Stop.

521
00:37:07,747 --> 00:37:08,622
Hyeong-wook!

522
00:37:08,706 --> 00:37:09,790
Hyeong-wook, no!

523
00:37:09,874 --> 00:37:11,459
Stop!

524
00:37:28,642 --> 00:37:31,228
No!

525
00:37:36,442 --> 00:37:37,443
Hyeong-wook.

526
00:37:41,822 --> 00:37:43,074
Hyeong-wook.

527
00:37:55,544 --> 00:37:56,796
Hyeong-wook!

